                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote script="textualis" scope="sole">
                                <p>The fragment is written in an <term type="script">Icelandic
                                    gothic bookhand</term>. The hand is identical with the main hand of <ref
                                        type="ms" target="AM02-0045-en">AM 45 fol.</ref> (<bibl><ref
